      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"complex\" is a bit of a cop out lol. like if you look at the actual data, isn't it pretty clear that the social justice side is backed by more recent sociological studies while the \"deterrence\" thing is kinda just an old way of thinking that doesnt really work anymore?",
